{"tid":1727732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今期流行：割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:40:06.000Z","uid":97600,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f786dc01639600e440cdcbdcfe9e938b47930da5","tid":1727732,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"大家係咪當咗不割蓆、不分化、不篤灰、不抹黑、不捉鬼係口號黎？<br />\n咁之前大家一直堅持緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n好心大家唔好中「中計黨」搞出黎啲矛招兼手段啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地對家曱近平係佢間豬欄到笑到見牙唔見眼啦，醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟我讀一次：「本人 承諾 不割蓆、不分化、不篤灰、不抹黑、不捉鬼！」<br />\n做到呢啲野先係一個合格既黃絲黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上去俾大家睇啦，仲望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ea759f16272914f1237aa0f5e7ae862f0ad0e4","tid":1727732,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03fa4189a30f7f01a7356e83cfed40fdca2129","tid":1727732,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1fccf7eadcca533c6a7ebd36a4c990c2bcf1fb","tid":1727732,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baafc32d3c24cc7b9f5f88bde6502906880891bd","tid":1727732,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br /